episodes.title: House of Prayer Leader Arrested  FBI Raid, Cult Allegations & Stolen Identity
episodes.description:
The mysterious leader of the House of Prayer Christian Church, known as Rony Denis, has been arrested after an FBI raid in Columbia County, Georgia. Federal prosecutors say he stole his identity, scammed veterans, and ran a nationwide fraud scheme. His bond hearing is underway as shocking new details emerge.
